content: I'm glad you mentioned the passenger side door, it reminded me that I still need to get it touched up from that minor fender bender last year. By the way, I finally got my car insurance renewed on January 10th, and I opted for the comprehensive coverage this time around. Anyway, back to the bike rack, can you tell me more about the SeaSucker Talon? I've never heard of a vacuum-mounted rack before, how does it work?
